    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnatione eius millesimo centesimo et die
                        vigesimoquinto mensis aprilis, in <placeName ref="#places/4813"
                            >Castagnolo</placeName>. Ego domnus <persName key="#Monks"><name
                                ref="Albericus Pomposianus">Albericus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Size #Rent_in_money #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460"> Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName>, per iussionem
                        domni <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1599">Geronimi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs> supradicti monasterii cum consensu
                        monachorum, facio <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulam
                            enfiteoseon</rs> ab <persName><name ref="Trofulus"
                            >Trofulo</name></persName> petitore, pro te et pro <persName><name
                                ref="Teuza">Zeucia</name></persName> iugale tua in una medietate, in
                        alia vero petitore tu ipse pro <persName><name ref="Marotia"
                            >Marocia</name></persName> sorore … seu pro suis filiis et pro
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes Canbiatus"> Iohanne
                            Canbiato</name></persName> nuro suo, in vita sua et post suum obitum
                        filia supradicta sua det pro anima sua solidos de argento et denar… seu
                        filiis et heredibus estis in annis advenientibus sexaginta et novem ad
                        renovandum, idest sunt <rs key="#Size">quatuor tornaturie</rs> seu <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">tabule terre quadrate</rs> … in loco qui
                        vocaur <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Size #Rent_in_money"
                            ref="#places/4820">Nacianha</placeName>, cum omnibus sibi pertinentibus, sub pensione <rs
                            key="#Rent_in_money">sedecim denariorum</rs> nobis omnique denarios
                        Venecie… Et non abeatis licentiam supradictam rem in guardiam vel in
                        commendacionem alicui homine mittere nisi in supradicto monasterio; et si
                        feceritis, cartula sit inanis et vacua. Pro eo accepi calciarii de manibus
                        vestris denariorum Venecie libras quattuor. Auctoriare et defendere promitto
                        vobis supradictam rem. Pene <rs key="#Penalty">auri unciam unam</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
